I'll use 16 cells per direction (as implied by the original plan wanting 32 everywhere, but let me check - the user said "Use 32 grid points in all directions", so I'll make blocks with 32 subdivisions).

Actually, looking at the user requirement: "domain extent is 1x1x1. Use 32 grid points in all directions." So each block should have 32 cells in appropriate directions.

